  "keyFeatures": [
    "70+ stateless developer tools accessible via MCP stdio or interactive CLI/TUI",
    "Media processing pipeline (image, video, audio, PDF) powered by DevPixelForge (Rust)",
    "Design tools: layout analysis, design token management, color palette generation",
    "AI-powered tools via Gemini API: UI image generation and screenshot-to-Markdown conversion",
    "Security & cryptography: hashing, HMAC, JWT, password hashing, key generation, secret masking",
    "Works with Claude Desktop, Cursor, and any MCP-compatible AI client",
    "Fully stateless — no database, no embeddings, no persistent state",
    "Zero CGO dependencies; installable via Homebrew or built from source"
